    p for example

    form.example-form
        p 使用matInput的errorStateMatcher属性，覆盖（默认情况下，当控件无效并且用户与元素进行了交互（触摸）或父表单已经提交时，将显示这些错误消息。）
        mat-form-field.example-full-width
            input(matInput="", placeholder="Email", [formControl]="emailFormControl", [errorStateMatcher]="matcher")
            |
            mat-hint Errors appear instantly!
            |
            mat-error(*ngIf="emailFormControl.hasError('email') && !emailFormControl.hasError('required')")
                | Please enter a valid email address
            |
            mat-error(*ngIf="emailFormControl.hasError('required')")
                | Email is
                strong required

